  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: if you change Main Currency in Profile, and then request or send tokens or ETH in 1-1 chat - ~ 0 is shown, so the amount is not converted neither to USD neither to currency selected by user in Profile. All previous /request and /send command are shown ~0 USD after changing Main Currency.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ntwo possible scenarios:\r\n- amount is shown as converted to USD \r\n- amount is shown as converted to selected in \"Main currency\"\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n~0 USD\r\n![wram](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/33398967/41840048-6ad59622-786d-11e8-91a1-4f8407eb017a.png)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Profile\r\n- Change default currency ( to \"AUD\" for example)\r\n- Reopen app\r\n- Open 1-1 chat with any contact \r\n- Request ETH\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: [release build 14](https://jenkins.status.im/job/status-react/job/public-beta-1-testfairy/14/)\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n* Network: Mainnet\r\n",
